<div class="mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns" typeof="mw:Extension/references" about="#mwt534" data-mw='{"name":"references","attrs":{"group":"","responsive":"1"},"body":{"html":""}}'><ol class="mw-references references"><li about="#cite_note-1" id="cite_note-1"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-1" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-1" class="mw-reference-text">Bowring believes her date of birth most likely to have been 973; Mulhern places it somewhere between 970 and 978, and Waley claims it was 978. See Bowring (2004), 4; Mulhern (1994), 257; Waley (1960), vii.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-ShiraneB293-2" id="cite_note-ShiraneB293-2"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-ShiraneB293_2-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-ShiraneB293_2-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-ShiraneB293_2-2"><span class="mw-linkback-text">3 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-ShiraneB293_2-3"><span class="mw-linkback-text">4 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-ShiraneB293-2" class="mw-reference-text">Shirane (2008b), 293</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Henshall24ff-3" id="cite_note-Henshall24ff-3"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Henshall24ff_3-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Henshall24ff_3-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Henshall24ff_3-2"><span class="mw-linkback-text">3 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Henshall24ff_3-3"><span class="mw-linkback-text">4 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Henshall24ff-3" class="mw-reference-text">Henshall (1999), 24–25</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Shirane215-4" id="cite_note-Shirane215-4"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Shirane215_4-0" re