. (1992). (46).</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Mulhern83ff-22" id="cite_note-Mulhern83ff-22"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Mulhern83ff_22-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Mulhern83ff_22-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Mulhern83ff_22-2"><span class="mw-linkback-text">3 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Mulhern83ff-22" class="mw-reference-text">Mulhern (1991), 83–85</span></li><li about="#cite_note-23" id="cite_note-23"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-23" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-23" class="mw-reference-text">qtd in Mulhern (1991), 84</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Royall-24" id="cite_note-Royall-24"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Royall_24-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-Royall_24-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Royall-24" class="mw-reference-text">Tyler, Royall. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://harvardmagazine.com/2002/05/murasaki-shikibu.html" id="mwAWs">"Murasaki Shikibu: Brief Life of a Legendary Novelist: c. 973 – c. 1014"</a>. (May 2002) <i id="mwAWw">Harvard Magazine</i>. Retrieved August 21, 2011.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-M258ff-25" id="cite_note-M258ff-25"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-M258ff_25-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-M258ff_25-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-M258ff_25-2"><span class="mw-linkback-text">3 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-M258ff_25-3"><span class="mw-linkback-text">4 </span></a><a href="./Murasaki_Shikibu#cite_ref-M258ff_25-4"><span class="mw-linkback-text">5 </spa